  "body": "# Bug Report\n\n## Problem\n\nI sent transactions that were expected to be included in hours. They are still visible on Etherscan, but Status dropped them from the Transaction history screen after a while and I don't know what status will do if they become confirmed.\n\n#### Expected behavior\n\nDon't drop transactions. Keep a record of each one initiated by the user, even if it is never included in the chain.\n\n#### Actual behavior\n\nDrops transactions (they disappear from Transaction history, even though they were there initially).\n\n### Reproduction\n\nSee above\n\n### Additional Information\n\n- Status version: 0.13\n- Operating System: Android",
